title: Is Credit Suisse the new Lehman Brothers?

media:group.media:title: Is Credit Suisse the new Lehman Brothers?
media:group.media:description:
Concerns about the financial health of Credit Suisse over the weekend have led to market fears of another meltdown similar to Lehman Brothers’ collapse in 2008. Rumors spread on Twitter that Credit Suisse’s capital position is at great risk, and the shares fell to new lows on Monday and the cost of insuring the bank against default surged to its highest level in more than two decades before recovering later in the day.
